  "description": "Bring the decay potions and tipped arrow to java",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/use/installer/\"><img alt=\"fabric\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img alt=\"fabric-api\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/BoyPika/bring-decay\"><img alt=\"github\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://quiltmc.org/en/install/client/\"><img alt=\"quilt\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/quilt_vector.svg\"></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/qsl\"><img alt=\"quilted-fabric-api\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/quilted-fabric-api_vector.svg\"></a>\n<p>Adds the decay potion and tipped arrow to java edition</p>\n<p>The decay potions and arrows give the player the wither effect, just like bedrock edition.</p>\n<sub>It should be noted that due to the difference between bedrock and java the splash potion lasts longer than in bedrock</sub>",
